'''Frinka venom''' was a paralyzing agent taken from the fangs of [[frinka]], and used by [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] for live [[Bounty/Legends|bounties]]. [[Jodo Kast]] shot [[Nosstrick]] with a frinka venom dart on [[Fluwhaka]].

